02:52:38,399 --> 02:52:42,562
Reading these chapters is essential to clarify and simplify the difficult parts.

1054
02:52:42,562 --> 02:52:51,928
This way, even those with less education can understand, and the false teachings of Priscillian's error, condemned long ago under the sentence of anathema, can be clearly rejected.

1055
02:52:51,928 --> 02:53:11,232
